Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:17.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:21.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}看着撅起嘴的我
