Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你读到这封信的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许已经不再是黑炎掌控者了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为根据玛雅预言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到2012年  笼罩世界的毁灭波动将会吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并使你的精神波动变得衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你或许会看透一切  选择放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沦为一个仅会享受眼前之物的愚蠢的凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在已预感到了这样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以写下了这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被蒙蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有着特殊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被黑暗君主——邪王所选中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是普通人  你是独一无二的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初二的时候  寄给两年后的自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊  像白痴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从附近的游戏厅拿的游戏币
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有什么力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是无所谓啦  可这么晚了你要去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接六花回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游同学… 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想对她说的  想为她做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我二代邪王真眼  有话要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  爸爸已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心还没来得及做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为直到爸爸去世的那个早上为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都以为  爸爸很快就会好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那时  我遇到了勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花以前就见过我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  邪王真眼在两年前就已与你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时她在圣料理人的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你可以去跟爷爷奶奶一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气变得黏稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着…  就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  她每天都注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在监视我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是六花就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够像你那样思考真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起压抑感情  乖乖听话的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要率直很多  帅气很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的中二病是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花是被中二病拯救的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遇到你之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的中二病和你坚强的信念产生了憧憬的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在见识到你的力量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图去模仿你的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才选择了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才非你不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得浇水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游六花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  邪王真眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有样东西要给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伴  把枪拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回到那无聊的现实中去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想要和我一起改变现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦  演坏蛋演坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸一下哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是有内情的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐小凸家的车来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要换我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借黑炎掌控者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那都是船的灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是灯光而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发吧  现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迸裂吧  神经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是无形境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光芒正在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来吧  说出你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出你那一直无法传达的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说  中二病是很丢人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再也不想回想起来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想抹掉那些回忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当初那个疯癫的自己  真的会就此消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妄想着自己被别人监视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为自己设定角色  并忘我地去演绎的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有时候会口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想着世界会突然改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假想那遥远的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脑海中描绘出一场惊天动地的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是人们由生至死  不断重复着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永无止境地重复着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲  羞涩  却又令人怜爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为「自我意识过剩」的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为「自我」的必经之路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人这一生  都是中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病果然还是好难为情
